  npcName: Susan
  dialogueLines:
  - Hi there, i'm Susan
  - Are you from Medius ? also know as the Hub World
  - You are!! Do you know my husband ? his name is Joe, he's a Farmer and he loves
    apples
  - 'I miss him, but I''m glad your fixing the fractures '
  - I dont want to see him anytime soon
  - well its was nice to meet you, make sure to grab you key befor you level, it
    unlocks a hidden fortune
  - I tried to bring my riches to the afterlife, turns out there no use for it here
  - well bye!
